{
  "title": "ASI Backbone",
  "version": "2.0.2",
  "upload_type": "software",
  "description": "AsiBackbone is a .NET package-family project providing framework-neutral governance primitives for consequential software decision flow, including actor context, constraint evaluation, governance decisions, acknowledgment workflows, audit residue, durable outbox persistence, provider-neutral governance emission, OpenTelemetry projection, and signing-provider boundaries. Version 2.0.2 is a compatible patch release on the simplified AsiBackbone package and namespace line that corrects package icon presentation metadata and assets.",
